ppened?","answer":"Absolutely.","docId":"130916pmt","qSentId":388,"aSentId":389},{"question":"But anger manifested into violence by a gun?","answer":"Absolutely.","docId":"130916pmt","qSentId":407,"aSentId":408},{"question":"What\u0027s the answer?","answer":"Well, I think the answer is to really takes a look at these cases and see are there common threads in there.","docId":"130916pmt","qSentId":411,"aSentId":412},{"question":"What is your reaction?","answer":"Well, here is one thing it was shocking to me and it go back a lot of memories from November 5th 2009.","docId":"130916pmt","qSentId":423,"aSentId":424},{"question":"If you can\u0027t even get those kind of things in any kind of sensible gun control legislation what hope is there?","answer":"Well, right now, today it appears that there is no hope, but there is hope and there\u0027s light at the end of tunnel.","docId":"130916pmt","qSentId":428,"aSentId":429},{"question":"It is the preferred mass shooters weapon of choice, and yet I don\u0027t see any logical reason and you\u0027re a military man why any civilian needs to have one of these killing machines?","answer":"Well, a lot of civilians they purchase one because what you have to look at, Piers is that a lot of times different fractions glorify in AR15 or in automatic rifle.","docId":"130916pmt","qSentId":436,"aSentId":437}]